description:
Description du poste: We are looking for a Production Supervisor - Docteur en Pharmacie.

Responsibilities:

Organize workflow by assigning responsibilities and preparing schedules;
Set daily/weekly/monthly objectives and communicate them to employees;
Check production output according to specifications;
Oversee and coach employees;
Ensure the safe use of equipment and schedule regular maintenance;
Submit reports on performance and progress;
Identify issues in efficiency and suggest improvements;
Train new employees on how to safely use machinery and follow procedures;
Enforce and respect strict safety guidelines, GMPs and company standards;

Description du profil recherché: Requirements and skills:

Docteur en Pharmacie with 1 to 3 years in similar role;
Experience in using various types of Pharma manufacturing machinery and tools;
Organizational and leadership abilities;
Communication and interpersonal skills;
Self-motivated with a results-driven approach;
Problem-solving skills.

"In accordance with the provisions of the GDPR and other legislation in force on personal data protection, the contracting company guarantees that the processing of your personal data is lawful, fair, transparent, and limited to the purposes for which your data was collected."

